version.provenance: Selected parent SNOMED-CT condition and included descendants (standard codes only).  Apply clinical review result, removed concepts that should not be included in the  Incorporates domain team feedback. Responding to domain team
version.limitations: May not include certain medications or procedures that may signal a condition. Also note that only standard concepts are included, so should be applied to only the harmonized data. Notion of "complicated" (or not) is based on the intention of the Charlson definition of "diabetes with chronic complications."
